name: Julie Keane Aviation
about: Julie Keane Aviation, located at the Ramona Airport in California, is a reputable flight school led by Julie Keane, a seasoned flight instructor with over 20 years of experience. The school benefits from the airport's inland location, which provides a favorable climate for flying. Julie Keane Aviation offers a range of training programs, including Private Pilot, Commercial Pilot, and Flight Instructor certifications, as well as Instrument Flight Instructor training. The school is committed to providing high-quality flight training in a supportive and professional environment, ensuring students receive the best possible education to achieve their aviation goals. With a focus on safety and excellence, Julie Keane Aviation is an ideal choice for aspiring pilots.
